<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1058,1187,1237]" pageId="14" pageNumber="1159">
E t y m o l o g y: The specific epithet, 
<emphasis box="[567,636,1188,1209]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="1159">aspera</emphasis>
, is a Latin adjective with the meaning of &quot;rough&quot;; with reference to the coarse macrosculpture on the pronotum.
</paragraph>
